dc_title_s: Map of the counties of Alpena, Presque Isle and Montmorency and parts of Alcona, Oscoda, Crawford, Otsego, and Cheboygan compiled and drawn by Victor G. Burnham.
dc_description_s: Shows major cities and towns. Shows railroads. 1 map: col.; 82 x 90 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
